<tr>
<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">There is a squad ring from a halfling quest in Rivervale you can get if you are a halfling. It will heal 80hp and is rechargeable by a cleric in RV supposedly. I got the ring - you just have to kill a TON of goblins and orcs... and I do mean a TON. <p>

The best way for warriors to heal is to bind wounds using bandages (bought from vendors, kinda expensive at lower levels though). That can heal you to 50% health much faster than just sitting. <p>

Other than that... group with a healer! =) <p>

Hope this helps.</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
