<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">The ring also drops off the guards and I don't know anything about a quest to recharge it.  But with a war you can solo to 20 if you get a lot of hp items and lots of bandages.  Get yourself low then bandage to halfway then take off your hp stuff and bandage some more.  if you have good HP stuff once you put it back on you will have 70%+ health.  Works best with monk as you can top yourself off with mend.<p>

obwin<br>
54enchanter<p>

